Package: imgbif
Type: Package
Title: Pre-process and write images from GBIF multimedia files and classify them manually with Shiny apps
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Brenton Bruns
Maintainer: Brenton Bruns <brenton.joey.bruns@pyhsik.uni-giessen.de>
Description: This package allows for the pre-processing of multimedia files obtained from GBIF database downloads.
    Additionally, the package offers functionality for downloading images utilizing parallel processing for enhanced efficiency.
    Moreover, the images can be manually classified with Shiny apps.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
